'I have so many clothes it's ridiculous but looking good and feeling good in our clothes is a big deal. Wearing the right clothes can make you go from feeling just OK to feeling great, which was the feeling behind my collection.' 

Casey, who has her own  walk-in-wardrobe at home, says that launching her own range of clothes and accessories is a 'dream come true'.  

