Casey loved creating her own fashion range so much that she already has her sights set on designing a shoe collection. 

'Shoes are my weakness,' she said. 'If I go to buy one pair, I always walk away with at least three or four. I would love to join up with a designer and properly design my own range, from heels to boots to wedges. I am definitely a shoe-a-holic.'

The star isn't limited to just fashion design and has been busy shooting a film called Bonded By Blood, which is out later this year.

