'I'm very excited for you all to see this because people don't know that I am a trained actress. This is going to be a great way for people to see me in a different light as it's a very serious role - it's actually based on a true story,' she said.

'I also have my radio show, which I co-present with Sam Dowler every Saturday on Vibe107.6. It's lots of fun and we talk about lots of showbiz gossip and the events and premieres we have been to that week.

'I am hoping for my acting to take off and that is what I'm focussing on so who knows; in five years maybe I will be in Hollywood!'.

The preview of Casey's Closet for Honeyz.com will launch today. The full collection will be available from 1st April.  

 

